Why I reject Eagles: Hole in the World:
- It’s too concise and mood‑uniform to satisfy my desire for a full, album‑style listening experience with varied dynamics and instrumental variety. While its harmonies and organic production are attractive, the limited scope (single/EP, somber tone) offers little stylistic variety and less of the forward momentum created by richer, multi‑textured arrangements.
Why I select Can't Slow Down:
