Why I reject Styx: Greatest Hits
- Styx leans toward theatrical, progressive and arena‑rock territory: Although Styx offers strong harmonies and clear instrumental interplay (keys, guitars), the theatrical, progressive‑leaning singles and bold dynamic contrasts point toward the bombastic, arena‑oriented style I explicitly dislike. That style tends to prioritize big anthems and high‑impact dynamics rather than the intimate, reflective mood I seek.
