- Styx’s strengths are not the priority for me: The strong production, theatrical dynamics and prog lean are laudable, but they appeal less to my core tastes (intimacy, subdued organic production, reflective lyricism, harmony‑centered arrangements) and more to a stadium/anthem aesthetic I avoid.
